CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 12, 1955, pg. 20, reads: "Famous TV Set for Laquilla's New Room - gift of Sylvania... picture includes James W. Lindberg, sales promotion manager; William W. Baker, sales manager; William G. Nunn, Pittsburgh Courier; Henry C. Givan Jr., president of C. R. Rogers Corp., wholesale distributors for Sylvania in this area, and Herman T. Smith, national sales consultant for Sylvania."
TitMainTitle: William G. "Bill" Nunn and two other men standing around Sylvania Halolight television set for Laquilla Foster, in Sylvania display with record players and TVs
